{"tid":748323,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"面上祛斑方法","createTime":"2018-07-19T06:25:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T18:50:09.000Z","uid":169700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e60dbab9d453c46a28053e49471d0d93ed13205c","tid":748323,"uid":169700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:25:16.000Z","msg":"細個唔聽呀媽話冇用防曬已經有雀班<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家越大越多同深色 就算用左防曬都係唔夠<br />\n再加上青春期既陳年暗瘡印<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想求 面上祛斑方法 有咩護膚品有效<br />\n有諗過做激光 但唔知邊度好 求介紹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098f8c95a5fc9929028131c4b569c020c63ba382","tid":748323,"uid":146654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T14:46:16.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95ddc09b90b4d5501f21d16dd8aace010ad303b9","tid":748323,"uid":21757,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T18:50:09.000Z","msg":"首先唔好再有新雀斑，慢慢處理舊有的<br />\n防曬要用得適當，就算產品度數幾高都要三至四小時補加，如果太多面油丶汗就2-3小時補加<br />\n外出加帽或擔遮<br />\n<br />\n內服美白產品，每天再用美白精華<br />\n美白面膜功效大致分兩種<br />\n  一  美白去斑<br />\n  二   當日曬黑當日敷，壓制黑色素增長<br />\n<br />\n激光係最快有效去斑方法，做後都要做防曬"}]}